Thank you for choosing Audlis, the audiobook app that respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our app.

1. Information We Do Not Collect

Audlis is committed to maintaining your privacy. We do not collect any personal information, including but not limited to names, email addresses, phone numbers, or any other personally identifiable information. We believe in a privacy-first approach, ensuring that your usage of Audlis remains completely anonymous.

2. Data Collection

Audlis does not engage in any data collection practices. We do not track your listening habits, preferences, or any other user-specific information. Your audiobook choices and usage patterns remain private and are not shared with any third parties.

3. Account Creation

Audlis is a free app that does not require any user account creation. You can enjoy our audiobook services without providing any personal information. This means you can listen to your favorite books without the need for account sign-ups, ensuring your privacy is never compromised.

4. Device Information

Audlis may collect non-personal information about the devices on which you install and use our app. This information is general and helps us improve the performance and user experience of Audlis. However, this data does not contain any personally identifiable information.

5. Communication

Audlis does not send you any promotional emails or messages. We respect your privacy and will only contact you in response to specific inquiries or support requests initiated by you.

6. Third-Party Services

Audlis does not integrate with any third-party services or platforms that may compromise your privacy. We do not share any data with external partners, advertisers, or analytics services.

7. Updates to the Privacy Policy

Audlis may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Any changes to the Privacy Policy will be posted in the app, and we encourage you to review it periodically.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions, concerns, or feedback about our Privacy Policy or our app in general, please contact us at [insert contact email].

By using Audlis, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. We appreciate your trust in us and are committed to ensuring the privacy and security of your information.

Thank you for choosing Audlis!
